Revision history for Perl extension Perl-PowerToys

0.14 Mon 11 May 2009
	- Adding --author support to ppi_copyright

0.13 Sun 10 May 2009
	- Upgrading to Module::Install::DSL 0.87
	- Adding new ppi_copyright tool

0.12 Thu 30 Apr 2009
	- Upgrading to Module::Install::DSL 0.83
	- Adding support for "our $VERSION";
	- Adding support for all four quote variants

0.11 Thu  6 Mar 2008
	- Upgrading to Module::Install 0.76
	- Adding increment support
	- Bug fixes

0.10 Sun 16 Nov 2007
	- VERSION detection supports fully referenced variables
	  (now in the change command as well)
	- Refactored ppi_version into PPI::App::Version

0.09 Fri  2 Nov 2007
	- VERSION detection supports fully referenced variables

0.08 Thu 12 Jul 2007
        - If PPI::Document fails for a document, skip it
        - Add a Usage message if no command
        - Add a show command

0.07 Wed  9 May 2007
        - Upgrading to use File::Find::Rule::Perl
        - Upgrading to Module::Install 0.67

0.06 Sun 19 Mar 2006
	- Renaming to PPI-PowerToys for better clarity
	- Changing ppichangeversion to ppi_version to allow the addition
	  or more features in future versions.

0.05 Sun 22 Jan 2006
	- Skip files we can't write to

0.04 Sun 15 Jan 2006
	- Allow _ in ppichangeversion versions

0.03 Wed 11 Jan 2006
	- Added .t files to the list checked

0.01 Wed 11 Jan 2006
	- Created initial version
